{"type": "article", "id": 30393, "title": "树脂灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-01T23:05:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160801163646OVDyn9LX0lmNAfPU.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>这些由三个独立部分组成的三角形树脂台灯 Painterly Spectrum 是日本设计师 <a href=\"http://cargocollective.com/taegnishimoto\" rel=\"nofollow\">Taeg Nishimoto</a> 的最新作品，点亮之后就像是实体化的彩虹。为了制作出这些五彩的灯罩，Nishimoto 先在羊皮纸上用乳胶漆进行创作，在干燥过程中再将环氧树脂涂在表面。羊皮纸会在完全干燥后移除，留下成型的树脂以及乳胶的独特质感。台灯高约 30 到 40 厘米，厚度仅为 3 毫米，不同颜色组件可以自由组合，白天也可以作为一件漂亮的装饰品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801170203o7QirRzpUSqhdMml.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684597\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608011702050D5Ijqef8p49R6QG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.641809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801170210uBXGtPeUVI0JnTjx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.880196\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801170145XVCbxzf5Bg0Udp3K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.370416\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}